Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Futon, clothes, shoes, toothbrush...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, don't go and pull disappearing acts like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It scares me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, pick a green one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be safer if we hold hands while we walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Safer for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the blue one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when were there so many parents with children here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Okay. Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What size are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to be comparing it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit waving your arms around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyjamas! Pants! Shirts! Socks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want a skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only put trousers in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't let us wear skirts to nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nursery!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's Monday, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little further. Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost home, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you bunking off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You good for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always bringing me stuff I don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean? Damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the Maeda residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello. I heard about your recent loss, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko-san? It's Daikichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Haruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I never asked for your mobile number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you go about starting nursery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nursery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? You actually took Rin-chan home with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "for now"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's too late for me to take the day off tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the procedure to enrol her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just enrol her right away, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you pull some strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I'm the right person to be asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You could start by asking someone at the city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sunday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just something on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,Mama, is that Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:37.94,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.81,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a temporary nursery for emergencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A temporary nursery for emergencies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! Rin-chan! Rin-chan! Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, just something on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be done in a minute. Just wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko-san, I'm taking the miso soup off the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it sounds like you're pretty busy, so I'll call back la{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, hardly any results...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, suddenly I'm going to double my work commute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's pretty close, but I can't get out of work at six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.65,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sure. Let's play again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bye bye, Reina-chan! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This one looks pretty good,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but it says they'll only take kids on emergency notice for ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The futon feels strangely warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, about the nursery you're going to today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.11,Alt,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Elbows off the table while you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The nursery you're going to is only\Ntaking you on a temporary basis, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Temporary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you'll go there until we can find a place to formally enrol you at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "formally" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It means properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's slightly different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, {\i1}my{\i0} hair's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Put me down! Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it embarrassing for you to have other kids see me carrying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of her, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We will. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to make it back while it's light,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll try to be as quick as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pinky promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell a lie, I'll absolutely swallow a thousand needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger was cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the song wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See you. Wait for me, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rin. I never thought about how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You had no understanding of your mum's\Ncircumstances, nor of my granddad's lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You only knew the pain of being left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I was going to leave you behind, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure having that happen to you once...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...is more than enough to last you a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Read this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san, let's grab some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got mine a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then I'll be back in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The first day of the month and you're already in workaholic mode, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me a photo of this sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san! There's a call for you on line four about the investors' inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kawachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, don't break it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miyata-san from Mitsutomo Trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? This is Kawachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Kawachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be done at work in just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The nursery is... so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin! Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are those crisps? They look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopped vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I swallowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...a thousand needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi-san! You need to sign here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's actually likely,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but what if I find a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi. This was supposed to go out yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This really isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already apologised to the recipient, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll call them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for a few drinks. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, tonight's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something going on then, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it. Sounds like someone's getting lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Run away from the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How long can I keep living like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Rin-chan's things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all that she has in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother and child health record and\Nother important documents are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's only for a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,raising a child is a terribly difficult job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, Rin is the one who has it the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm just going to have a little look in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mouth's still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the relatives talk about you\Nlike you're some sort of supervillain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder... Who's the real villain, Masako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've decided to sleep over there aft{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? D-Did I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweat. Sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll change the sheets, so give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that it's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Rin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan is going to English school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Daikichi, you are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Daikichi looks tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,On the train ride back home, he's always snoring like an engine.
